# CtrlDehNet
Follow-Your-Prompt: Controllable Image Dehazing via Latent Space Manipulation
<img src='https://github.com/CVhnu/CtrlDehNet/blob/main/ctrl.png'>

# Dependencies and Installation
Ubuntu >= 18.04  
CUDA >= 11.0  
Python 3.6  
Pytorch 1.2.0  

\# git clone this repository
git clone[(https://github.com/CVhnu/CtrlDehNet.git) ](https://github.com/CVhnu/CtrlDehNet.git)

\# create new anaconda env
conda create -n ctrldehnet python=3.8  

# Get Started
1. Download the pretrained checkpoints.
2. Preparing data for training

# Quick test
python inference.py 


## The released model can be downloaded at
[(Download)](https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1BrYoGgqyrY_NUlJ-U4qn7h3aNQXvn5uy?usp=drive_link)


